{"tid":756374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"分享自己一個故事 我老竇係有錢佬","createTime":"2018-07-26T03:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T04:07:54.000Z","uid":183148,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f132e3ec14292d7b7182c7a737e615ad607f94f2","tid":756374,"uid":183148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:59:09.000Z","msg":"人冇乜生存目的 不過好彩有既係錢 有時覺得 雖然老竇冇乜俾關愛我 但至少有洗唔曬既錢 嫖賭飲吹16歲已經試過曬 有父幹真好"},{"pid":"0467d1cb09d8006ef1973b807efa6e2fe8f769fe","tid":756374,"uid":123657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"既然係咁，點解唔試下做善事。當街派錢？"},{"pid":"e0cdbc111a4d50a0107956258474910ae01ca631","tid":756374,"uid":183148,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0467d1cb09d8006ef1973b807efa6e2fe8f769fe","tid":756374,"uid":123657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"既然係咁，點解唔試下做善事。當街派錢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T04:10:02.000Z","msg":"派錢就冇試過 不過助養佐30個細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得閒會同佢地寫下信交流"},{"pid":"b29f27e594868e4005de63e3bf24c5c6eed67ce3","tid":756374,"uid":71058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:01:34.000Z","msg":"可唔可以幫下流浪動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc378f138393c0469ac1e16ad5b0fed5d96eb4e3","tid":756374,"uid":14087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2180cabb5f7254adacb9e4dfc81ab98a4c778999","tid":756374,"uid":139203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e0cdbc111a4d50a0107956258474910ae01ca631","tid":756374,"uid":183148,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0467d1cb09d8006ef1973b807efa6e2fe8f769fe","tid":756374,"uid":123657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"既然係咁，點解唔試下做善事。當街派錢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T04:10:02.000Z","msg":"派錢就冇試過 不過助養佐30個細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得閒會同佢地寫下信交流"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"我都有！！！培幼會？"},{"pid":"b74ad28798e3d38515ee2ba48fcfb40e56648521","tid":756374,"uid":82829,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:15:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係一個被親生老竇老母遺棄既孤兒仔<br />\n算好彩俾一戶香港人家領養<br />\n可惜成長過程一直無家人既陪伴 教養 關愛<br />\n經歷兩次被寄養 <br />\n第一次係寄住係鄉下遠房親戚屋企 因為還小 什麼也不用想 所以能不錯地度過人生天真爛漫既7年 <br />\n到8歲那年 隨即迎來又一轉折 寄住係阿叔阿嬸既屋企 一住就係9年 從來無感受過所謂家人既關愛 人開始長大 終於發現內心個份空虛 缺愛 <br />\n於是 很早想找一個人係身邊 可以關心下自己 愛下自己 成長的階段 談了幾次戀愛 也被傷害了幾次<br />\n從沒有家人可哭訴 曾經最愛最刻骨銘心的戀人 也離我而去<br />\n一年又一年 依然被陰影所籠罩<br />\n<br />\n誰人會愛我這種孤兒仔 流落到谷底⋯<br />\n<br />\n有時我會諗 真的不想再活了</blockquote><br />\nquote from 樓主舊po"},{"pid":"50af14901fc659910becfe5eccda954dc974a9df","tid":756374,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:45:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ec0ebbce3dc4ba3248a46609c377c65f541f334","tid":756374,"uid":183148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dc378f138393c0469ac1e16ad5b0fed5d96eb4e3","tid":756374,"uid":14087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:31:41.000Z","msg":"我讀得書少 個學位都係我老竇買俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好冇癮"},{"pid":"da3c8de12e0b4386a7a9a560f8b8321aab294249","tid":756374,"uid":183148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b74ad28798e3d38515ee2ba48fcfb40e56648521","tid":756374,"uid":82829,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:15:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係一個被親生老竇老母遺棄既孤兒仔<br />\n算好彩俾一戶香港人家領養<br />\n可惜成長過程一直無家人既陪伴 教養 關愛<br />\n經歷兩次被寄養 <br />\n第一次係寄住係鄉下遠房親戚屋企 因為還小 什麼也不用想 所以能不錯地度過人生天真爛漫既7年 <br />\n到8歲那年 隨即迎來又一轉折 寄住係阿叔阿嬸既屋企 一住就係9年 從來無感受過所謂家人既關愛 人開始長大 終於發現內心個份空虛 缺愛 <br />\n於是 很早想找一個人係身邊 可以關心下自己 愛下自己 成長的階段 談了幾次戀愛 也被傷害了幾次<br />\n從沒有家人可哭訴 曾經最愛最刻骨銘心的戀人 也離我而去<br />\n一年又一年 依然被陰影所籠罩<br />\n<br />\n誰人會愛我這種孤兒仔 流落到谷底⋯<br />\n<br />\n有時我會諗 真的不想再活了</blockquote><br />\nquote from 樓主舊po"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:35:18.000Z","msg":"我會話真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成長路上冇乜屋企人既關心 老竇所有嘢都會幫我安排曬 但永遠唔知我最缺係乜 老土d講句 真係窮得只剩錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心靈好空虛 都唔知人生有乜意義"},{"pid":"bc763904401c73ff940974e9a4b3f5f75ea38c95","tid":756374,"uid":183148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2180cabb5f7254adacb9e4dfc81ab98a4c778999","tid":756374,"uid":139203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e0cdbc111a4d50a0107956258474910ae01ca631","tid":756374,"uid":183148,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0467d1cb09d8006ef1973b807efa6e2fe8f769fe","tid":756374,"uid":123657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"既然係咁，點解唔試下做善事。當街派錢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T04:10:02.000Z","msg":"派錢就冇試過 不過助養佐30個細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得閒會同佢地寫下信交流"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"我都有！！！培幼會？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"宣明會 培幼會都有<br />\nbtw絲打都幾有愛心"},{"pid":"4f1ace1e6a7c5da87116a44591df93e3662be05c","tid":756374,"uid":139203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc763904401c73ff940974e9a4b3f5f75ea38c95","tid":756374,"uid":183148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2180cabb5f7254adacb9e4dfc81ab98a4c778999","tid":756374,"uid":139203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e0cdbc111a4d50a0107956258474910ae01ca631","tid":756374,"uid":183148,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":